Problem Statement¶

The purpose of this project is to understand and analyze used cars prices all over India and suggest the best used cars based on model year, fuel type, kms_driven, location and budget to the customers by using data mining techniques.¶

plt.show();

Observation¶

  • By analysing the above graph we can say that most of the car prices are in between 3-5 lakhs
  • The Graph shows that it is a normal distribution model

In [21]:
#boxplot
sns.boxplot(x="Price(In Lakhs)",data=df,width=0.9,linewidth=1,color="yellow",showmeans=True)
plt.title("Representation of Q1,Median,Q3,IQR and Outliers of  Car Prices")
plt.show();

observation¶

  • By examining the above graph we can say that
  • medain is approx 5lakhs
  • min price is 1.4 lakhs(approx)
  • max price is 9 lakhs(approx)
  • Q1(25%) of car prices is lie in between 1.4 - 3.5 lakhs
  • Median(50%) of car prices is 5lakhs (approx)
  • Q3(75%) of car prices is lie in between 1.4 - 6lakhs and remaining 25% of data is above Q3
  • Outliers found in between 9-16lakhs
  • Inter Quartile Range(IQR)= Q3-Q1 = 6-3.5=2.5
  • The plot shows that data is normally distributed
In [23]:
#boxplot
sns.boxplot(x="Kms",data=df,width=0.9,linewidth=1,color="pink",showmeans=True)
plt.title("Representation of Q1,Median,Q3,Median,IQR and Outliers of  Kms that driven by cars")
plt.show();

observation¶

  • medain is approx 32k kms
  • min kms is 1500(approx)
  • max kms is 83k(approx)
  • Q1(25%) of car prices is lie in between 1.5k -18k
  • Median(50%) of car prices is 31.5k(Kms)approx
  • Q3(75%) of car prices is lie in between 1.5k - 45k and remaining 25% of data is above Q3
  • NO Outliers found
  • Inter Quartile Range(IQR)= Q3-Q1 = 45-18=27
  • The plot shows that data is normally distributed

plt.show();

observations¶

  • By examining the above box plot from 2011 to 2016 Model Year is directly proportion to the Kms driven by car and from 2107 to 2019 the scenario became reverse i.e Model Year is indirectly proportional to the Kms driven by car
  • Max Kms driven by a car is in 2014 Year
